NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
J.D., JR., Defendant-Petitioner,
and
J.G., Defendant. In the Matter of J.D., III, a Minor-Respondent. C-268 September Term 2017
078479 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 2, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003716-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
